name: Dash FPS
description: Dash FPS isn't your average FPS. Our Players have the option to utilize Jetpacks, Super speed, and much more. We have added All-terrain vehicles and increased range on guns like the LMG. Now with many modes such as Capture the Flag, Solo, Team Deathmatch, ATV Conquest and more. With our new Full Multiplayer support you can join anyone online.
